 <!--Mathematical logic, model theory, o-minimal geometry.-->



<h2>Travel Awards  -  Summer School in Tame Geometry, Konstanz, July 18-23, 2016 </h2>  

Funding  towards accommodation and travel expenses is now available. Students and early postdocs are welcome to apply. Priority will be given to students. In order to apply, please submit your CV (including academic grades averages) and a short statement of purpose (addressing how attendance of the summer school fits your academic plans) to the email address below. In case of students, a letter of recommendation must also be submitted to the same address directly by your professor or academic supervisor.
<br> <br>

<b> Email address: </b> tame-geometry@uni-konstanz.de
<br> <br>

<b> Deadline: <font style="text-decoration:line-through;"> March 1  </font> April 1, 2016. </b> Screening of applications begins on submission, so early applications are strongly encouraged. Decisions are expected to be announced in April 2016.</b>

<br> <br>

If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us at the above email address.

<br><br>

<a href="http://www.math.uni-konstanz.de/~eleftheriou/summerschool/"> 
Back to Summer School</a>


